533
00:37:43,001 --> 00:37:45,004
relativist, 
altfel, am obţine acest

534
00:37:45,004 --> 00:37:47,002
număr ridicol
ce l-am calculat

535
00:37:47,002 --> 00:37:50,002
mai devreme,
mai mare decât viteza luminii.

536
00:37:50,002 --> 00:37:54,052
